snippet.title: PC Engine Longplay [242] Championship Rally
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Here's some rally!

There are 2 rally modes, so-called High Speed Rally and Adventure Rally. In time attack mode you can choose all the same tracks from these modes and beat your time so I omitted to record that.

at 31:51 the Adventure Rally mode starts. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
